    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"Finding a way to let go\" ... that's what it feels like. Like i'm just stuck in this loop of misery and there's no real way to actually make it stop. Everything feels heavy and pointless. I honestly just want to sleep and never have to wake up to this again. Is that even a crazy thing to want?",
